Description: Comprehensive web security testing suite
 Spectra is a powerful web security testing suite designed for ethical
 hackers and security professionals. It includes 15+ security modules
 for vulnerability detection, hash cracking, network monitoring, and more.
 .
 Key features:
  * SQL Injection, XSS, IDOR, XXE scanning
  * Advanced hash cracking with GPU support
  * Network traffic monitoring
  * Directory and subdomain discovery
  * Technology fingerprinting
  * Professional reporting capabilities
 .
 This tool is intended for authorized security testing only.